title: Underdog
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tiny hot dog shop that offers both organic sausage dogs as well as vegan dogs in several flavors. Each dog comes with choice of wheat or white bun, served plain. Help yourself to the toppings & condiment bar (mustard, ketchup, hot sauce, sauerkraut, raw onion, relish). The sides and desserts are all vegan suitable and might include potato salad, cole slaw, and sweets like cookies and pie. Couple small tables inside, or sit outside on the bench. Minimum charge with credit card required.
